name: the kiss
description: Taken in 2007 at Fosfobox Bar Club, Rua Siqueira Campos, 143 - Copacabana, Rio de Janeiro. Fosfobox opened in 2005 and closed in 2020 during the Covid-19 pandemic. It was one of the most diverse and respected nightclubs in Rio de Janeiro. Shot with Fuji Superia 1600. /// by KPLLO
